I cannot keep updating it, I will put a message on the UserStyles.org page.



In the case that I stop updating this style or you want to update the messages yourself,
I've decided to include code in a 2nd code section so you can manually change
the reminders without a huge hassle.

Follow the commented directions in this section, copy & paste code from the 2nd section.
You can CTRL+F to find the code you'll need by month, flight, or festival name.


*/

